			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing the life cycle inventory (LCI) data derived from this study, users should ensure that the specific processes captured reflect the environmental effects associated with the production of multi-Si ingots for solar application within the Chinese context from 2011 to 2016, as documented in the referenced literature. Consideration should be given to technological changes that may have occurred post-2016, which might alter the impact assessment outcomes. It is essential to account for methodological assumptions such as the inclusion or exclusion of recycling processes and the modelling of specific use-phase behaviors in the system under study. Users should also verify the consistency of the data with any updated national or international standards and regulations relevant to solar PV system manufacturing.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用本研究得出的生命周期清单（LCI）数据时，用户应确保所捕获的特定过程真实反映了2011至2016年间中国生产适用于太阳能的多晶硅铸锭的环境影响情况，如参考文献所记录。应考虑到2016年后可能发生的技术变化，这些变化可能会改变影响评估结果。必须考虑包括或排除回收过程以及在所研究系统中对特定使用阶段行为建模等方法论假设。用户还应核实数据与任何更新的国家或国际标准和法规的一致性，这些标准和法规与太阳能光伏系统制造相关。</useAdviceForDataSet>
